I'm... inside an inn...?[k]
@mu f=love
@fg c=マックス e=通常 f=01
[マックス f=01]「Oh, you're awake.」[k]
It seems that I am lying in a bed at an inn. [マックス] was standing beside me.[k]
[テオ f=12]「[マックス]... What happened...?」[k]
[マックス f=01]「[マルエット] came to me, frantically asking for help. She took me to the bottom of the valley, and there you were, bleeding. So I carried you here.」[k]
[テオ f=14]「I see... Thanks, [マックス].」[k]
I must have collapsed from the injury the dragon gave me.[k]
[マックス f=01]「You should thank [マルエット] too. She stayed up all night taking care of you, you know?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Um... [マルエット]...?」[k]
I glance over at the bed.[k]
[マルエット e=通常 f=19]「... ∗zzz∗」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
There was [マルエット], sleeping with her face buried in my bed.[k]
[マルエット f=19]「... ∗zzz∗」[k]
[テオ f=05]「[マルエット]...」[k]
Ah... You must have fallen asleep because you were so tired from taking care of me... I'm sorry...[k]
[マックス f=01]「Okay, I'll take off now.」[k]
@cl
[マックス] leaves the room. Only [マルエット] and I remain.[k]
[マルエット f=19]「... ∗zzz∗」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[マルエット] sleeps peacefully beside me, her head resting on the bed, breathing softly.[k]
Her innocent sleeping face really looks young.[k]
Her head, shoulders, and hands are so small that she looks too delicate to be fighting alongside us in an adventuring party.[k]
Such a small girl, with her large wings and thin arms, held me as I fell...[k]
What's more, she took such good care of me. Her sweetness made my heart melt.[k]
[テオ f=05]「[マルエット]...」[k]
I found myself irresistibly drawn to this girl, and gently stroked her hair.[k]
[マルエット v=vs252 f=65]「Aaa...」[k]
Then [マルエット], who had been asleep, woke up.[k]
[マルエット v=vs253 f=67]「Captain... ?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Sorry, I woke you up.」[k]
[マルエット v=vs254 f=02]「You're awake. Good...」[k]
Seeing my face, [マルエット] looks relieved.[k]
[テオ f=02]「I heard from [マックス]. He said you've been taking care of me the whole time...」[k]
[マルエット v=vs255 f=02]「No, it's... It's okay. Is your wound okay now?」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Yeah, thanks to you.」[k]
[マルエット v=vs256 f=09]「I was worried about you... The wound from the dragon was pretty deep...」[k]
[マルエット f=10]「...」[k]
[マルエット v=vs257 f=10]「I'm sorry... You were trying to protect me, and you got cut so deeply...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「It's fine. You saved my life afterwards, after all.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「If it weren't for you, I would have died. [マルエット], you saved my life.」[k]
[マルエット v=vs258 f=70]「That's... exaggerating things.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Hey, what happened to your wings?」[k]
[マルエット v=vs259 f=19]「I tucked them away ages ago. I can't leave them out for too long. It tires me out from the strain.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Hmm...」[k]
Apparently that's just how her wings work.[k]
[マルエット v=vs260 f=62]「Captain, don't do anything so reckless again! My wings aren't something I can just whip out whenever I want! Besides...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Besides?」[k]
[マルエット v=vs261 f=30]「...I was really worried. You didn't wake up at all...」[k]
; ↑ ボソボソとした声で
[テオ f=05]「[マルエット]...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I understand, I'll keep that in mind. I'm really sorry for worrying you.」[k]
[マルエット v=vs262 f=02]「Well... I just wanted you to understand...」[k]
I am a little surprised by her modesty, which she never shows normally.[k]
I was happy to see a different side of [マルエット] than usual.[k]
